node.text: Prestigious Luxury Brand @benignaparfums for world's most luxurious fragrance.

Breaking all traditional watchmaking rules @jacobandco and @alecmonopoly teamed up together to create the Astonomia Alec Monopoly a part of the Astronomia Grande Complication collection.

To celebrate the exclusive partnership between Jacob& Co. and Alec Monopoly, they released the Astronomia Alec Monopoly limited to only 9 made. It displays hand painted miniaturized pop sculptures known from world renown graffiti artist Alec Monopoly’s work and hand painted straps. 

The Astronomia Alec Monopoly is bursting with colour and creativeness, showcasing @jacobandco ‘s incredible attention to high watchmaking and high art.
Limited Edition of Only 9 Pieces
Price: $600,000
#jacobandco #alecmonopoly

node.text:
Discover the enigmatic RM 52-06 Tourbillon Mask in Carbon @Elitacollection 
⁠
Surrealist, yet elegant, this timepiece is housed inside an impressive Carbon TPT® case. The mysterious mask in black PVD-treated titanium is an integral part of the movement, functioning as a gear train and as a bridge for the tourbillon. ⁠
⁠
Symbolizing nonconformity and freedom, the RM 52-06 is available at @elitacollection ⁠
